    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3002">Iordanus</persName>, Dei
                        gratia <placeName ref="#places/173" key="#Cities">Capuae</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, concedimus, et confirmamus <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3000">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName>, constructo circa <rs key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversanae</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs>, et ad presens <persName ref="#people/3009"
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank">Ugone Badivello</persName>, eiusdem
                        monasterii <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> suisque successoribus, in perpetuum, videlicet
                            <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >curtes</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs>, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanos</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiteros</rs>, et nominati <persName key="#Priests"
                                ><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiterum</rs>, quae sunt prope <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >aquam</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Shores #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Mills #Coloni/tenants #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Priests"
                            ref="#places/695">Saonis</placeName>, et <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >molendina</rs>, cum clausuris et omnibus instrumentis eisdem molendinis
                        pertinentibus, in eodem Saone aedificata, et <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquas, et cursus
                            aquarum</rs> cum <rs key="#Shores">ripis</rs>, et cum introitu et exitu
                        suo, et cum omnibus <rs key="#Fisheries #Fish">piscationibus</rs>, et quid
                        quid ibi edificatum est, vel potest edificari, ad utilitatem monasterii,
                        quae fuerunt et pertinuerunt <persName key="#Palatine_count"
                            ref="#people/3073">Grimoaldo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Palatine_count">comiti palatii</rs>, et que ibi tenuerunt
                                <persName><name ref="Walpertus Hervenus">Gualterius
                            Haereveus</name></persName>, Brittorum conditores; et qualiter omnia
                        tenuit et dominatus est <persName ref="#people/3074">Guiglielmus de
                            Alno</persName>, qui, me concedente, ea omnia ante meam presentiam,
                        causa salutis animae meae et suae, dedit, tradidit atque obtulit praescripto
                        domino abbati, ad possessionem, et potestatem ac dominationem prescripti
                        monasterii, et domini abbatis suorumque successorum. Quod ego, benigno
                        favore concedens, huiusmodi litteris, nostri sigilli impressione sigillatis,
                        concedimus et confirmamus, ut iam supra scriptum est, omnia prenominata
                        predicto monasterio, et domino abbati suisque successoribus, remota omni
                        inquietudine, vel molestatione mortalium omnium. Quod si quis nostrae
                        concessionis et confirmationis paginam violare, facere irritare
                        presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">mille auri optimi libras</rs> persolvat,
                        medietatem nostro palatio, et medietatem prescripto monasterio, eiusque
                        rectoribus. Et soluta pena, hoc scriptum firmum et inviolabile maneat in
                        perpetuum; et ut firmius credatur, et diligentius observetur, nostro sigillo
                        fecimus sigillari. Scriptum <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173"
                            >Capuae</placeName>. Anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        millesimo octuagesimo quinto, per nonam indictionem, in publico instrumento
                        subscripti erant taliter subsignati. + Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Radulfus f. Aruini">Radulfus fìlius Erluini</name></persName>.
                        + Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Thomas">Tomas</name></persName>. +
                        Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Aruinus de Sancto Midando">Erluinus
                                de Sancto Midando</name></persName>.</ab>
